$ /dev/mdN

*md* stands for *meta disk* (but I've also seen: *multiple devices*).

? Linux supports the following *md devices*:
  • Linear
  • → Linux/filesystem/RAID 0, 1, 4, 5, 6, 10
  • Multipath
  • Faulty
  • Container

sa:

